txt.en: 'Good day to you. I am pleased that you have joined our guild. I am grateful you are willing to assist us with meeting the demands placed upon the guild. Food is a tie that binds together the lowliest and the wealthiest and we meet the requests of all.\n\n'As a member, we look to you to assist us in meeting requests set forth by the ever-demanding populace. Are you prepared to do your part?'
Craft a crate of cooked food for the Umbar Cook's Guild
The cook's guild in Umbar Baharbêl supplies foodstuff to taverns, the Kindred, and everyone in between. They require assistance with meeting the demands of the people.
Deliver a crate of food to the Umbar Cook's Guild Leader
Crafted a crate of cooked food for the Umbar Cook's Guild
Provide the cooked plates to the Umbar Cook's Guild Leader.
'Most excellent. This food will satisfy the needs of innkeeps in the lower quarters.'
The recipe needed to complete this quest is available for purchase. <rgb=#00f000>Purchase the quest recipe from the guild leader.</rgb>\n\nCreate a crate of cooked food for Umbar Baharbêl.
